      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this stunning, showroom-quality vehicle that is in absolute mint condition! This car has been meticulously cared for and looks as though it just rolled off the assembly line, featuring a flawless exterior and a pristine interior. If you are looking for the very best, this is the perfect opportunity to own a truly exceptional car that needs absolutely nothing.",
