    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major electronic features are fully functional. While there may be some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, it remains a dependable and presentable car for its next owner. You can expect a comfortable ride and a vehicle that is ready for the road without any immediate major repairs needed.",
