    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior still carries a great shine, though you may notice a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and some light surface scratches from normal car washes. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
